  "lyrics": [
    {
      "t": 0,
      "text": "And disciplinary remains mercifully",
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "t": 0,
      "text": "Yes and um, I’m with you, Derek, this star nonsense",
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "t": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes",
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "t": 0,
      "text": "Now which is it?",
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "t": 0,
      "text": "I am sure of it",
      "end": 79230
    },
    {
      "t": 79230,
      "text": "So, so you think you can tell",
      "end": 85990
    },
    {
      "t": 85990,
      "text": "Heaven from Hell?",
      "end": 89710
    },
    {
      "t": 89710,
      "text": "Blue skies from pain?",
      "end": 93980
    },
    {
      "t": 93980,
      "text": "Can you tell a green field from a cold steel rail?",
      "end": 102510
    },
    {
      "t": 102510,
      "text": "A smile from a veil?",
      "end": 106790
    },
    {
      "t": 106790,
      "text": "Do you think you can tell?",
      "end": 110910
    },
    {
      "t": 110910,
      "text": "Did they get you to trade your heroes for ghosts?",
      "end": 118780
    },
    {
      "t": 118780,
      "text": "Hot ashes for trees? Hot air for a cool breeze?",
      "end": 127020
    },
    {
      "t": 127020,
      "text": "Cold comfort for change?",
      "end": 131100
    },
    {
      "t": 131100,
      "text": "Did you exchange",
      "end": 134460
    },
    {
      "t": 134460,
      "text": "A walk-on part in the war for a lead role in a cage?",
      "end": 180530
    },
    {
      "t": 180530,
      "text": "How I wish, how I wish you were here",
      "end": 186990
    },
    {
      "t": 186990,
      "text": "We're just two lost souls swimming in a fishbowl, year after year",
      "end": 196350
    },
    {
      "t": 196350,
      "text": "Running over the same old ground, what have we found?",
      "end": 202830
    },
    {
      "t": 202830,
      "text": "The same old fears",
      "end": 206030
    },
    {
      "t": 206030,
      "text": "Wish you were here"
    }
  ],
